body_html:
Currently the TFLite converter doesn't support partially quantizing a model. We understand the need for this and plan to add support as we ramp up on other methods of quantization techniques.

So there isn't yet a tool for what you ask, but tools for better quantization options are on our roadmap.

Thanks!
